mapper.html:
Hi {{28.firstName}},

Thanks for signing up to the annual waitlist for Make Money With Make. I just tried to invite you in as we had an opening, but your account is showing "payment declined".

Sometimes cards can be finicky without addresses/etc and I usually don't ask for those (less friction). Probably on my end.

I'm going to send you a manual Stripe invoice in a sec. Would you mind paying it whenever you can? After, just let me know when it's sorted and I'll send you a manual invite into the community. Thanks again.

Cheers,
Nick
